data.description: This perfect blend of comfort and convenience offering an idyllic living experience for you. With 4 beds, 2 baths, and a spacious 2-car garage, this 1943 sqft. abode sits on a generous .26-acre lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The master bedroom is a true oasis, featuring an en-suite bathroom with a luxurious shower, and a dual sink vanity. A walk-in closet adds practicality to this private retreat. Embrace the advantages of the newly built block wall, which ensures your privacy and security, and the solar panels, which provide sustainable energy solutions. Solar is a power purchase agreement not a lease. Where comfort and convenience come together.
